\begin_layout Standard
We now focus on a particularly interesting facet of our problem, namely
 the amplitude and phase response of B2 under the influence of the driven
 particle B1.
 We study this experimentally for three different trap stiffness ratios
 of B1 and B2, the results of which are shown in Fig.
